* Content:
============

This directory contains a program that tests out the pipe function

------------------------------------------------------------------------

The program copies the content of the input.txt file into a new file
(output.txt) using the dynamically allocated buffor and pipe function.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Running the program:
=========================

The directory contains a makefile for the ease of compilation, as well
as cleaning and compressing the directory to an archive.

-> To run program:
       make run

-> To clean the directory (remove unwanted files):
       make clean

-> To compress the directory into a .tar.gz archive:
       make tar

========================================================================
